But in particular, before I do that, I want to thank Tufts University for coordinating a lot of judges. That takes a lot of effort to bring in the graduate students and allow the kids to have somebody to speak to who's in the field. Mr. Chris Mabbitt is here this evening. He also participates in the judging and coordinates judges from his firm.

10
