And before I introduce Kevin or allow him to speak, he actually was not at our local fair, because he was at the state fair, which they qualified for through the regional fair. So we coordinate with them to be able to get students to participate at higher level fairs. So Kevin's project, who worked with Kang and Travers, who I think is at a baseball game tonight,

